{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":857,"text":"Most people think"},{"time":5469,"text":"that new technology or advanced technology\ncan never start in Africa."},{"time":10149,"text":"Instead, they think that the best way\nto help the continent advance"},{"time":13877,"text":"is by providing aid or services"},{"time":16473,"text":"that the continent\ncan't provide for itself."},{"time":19864,"text":"So while we see advanced\ntechnology like robotics"},{"time":23217,"text":"and artificial intelligence"},{"time":24584,"text":"growing exponentially\nin the developed world,"},{"time":27416,"text":"those same people are worried"},{"time":28998,"text":"that a technologically backward\nAfrica is falling behind."},{"time":33190,"text":"That attitude couldn't be more wrong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37585,"text":"I'm a robotics entrepreneur\nwho's spent a lot of time here in Africa."},{"time":41433,"text":"And in 2014 we created Zipline,"},{"time":45777,"text":"which is a company that uses\nelectric autonomous aircraft"},{"time":49906,"text":"to deliver medicine to hospitals\nand health centers on demand."},{"time":53582,"text":"Last year, we launched the world's first\nautomated delivery system"},{"time":57777,"text":"operating at national scale."},{"time":59928,"text":"And guess what?"},{"time":61692,"text":"We did not do that in the US,"},{"time":64661,"text":"we didn't do it in Japan,"},{"time":66131,"text":"and we didn't do it in Europe."},{"time":68035,"text":"It was actually President Paul Kagame"},{"time":71282,"text":"and the Rwandan Ministry of Health"},{"time":74098,"text":"that made a big bet\non the potential of this technology"},{"time":77468,"text":"and signed a commercial contract"},{"time":79172,"text":"to deliver a majority\nof the country's blood on demand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83695,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":89395,"text":"Yeah, they deserve the applause."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92780,"text":"So why is blood important?"},{"time":94580,"text":"Rwanda collects between 60- and 80,000\nunits of blood a year."},{"time":98487,"text":"So this is a product\nthat when you need it,"},{"time":100511,"text":"you really, really need it."},{"time":102668,"text":"But blood is also challenging,"},{"time":104843,"text":"because it has a very short shelf life,"},{"time":107531,"text":"there are lots of different\nstorage requirements,"},{"time":110201,"text":"and it's really hard to predict the demand"},{"time":112585,"text":"for all of these different blood groups"},{"time":114531,"text":"before a patient actually needs something."},{"time":117477,"text":"But the cool thing is\nthat using this technology,"},{"time":120029,"text":"Rwanda has been able to keep\nmore blood centralized"},{"time":123585,"text":"and then provide it\nwhen a patient needs something"},{"time":126320,"text":"to any hospital or health center\nin an average of just 20 or 30 minutes."},{"time":131032,"text":"Do you guys want to see how it works?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":132863,"text":"(Audience) Yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134042,"text":"All right. Nobody believes me,\nso ... better to show."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136985,"text":"This is our distribution center,"},{"time":138533,"text":"which is about 20 kilometers\noutside of Kigali."},{"time":142340,"text":"This actually used to be a cornfield\nnine months ago,"},{"time":145312,"text":"and with the Rwandan government,"},{"time":146861,"text":"we leveled it and built this center\nin a couple weeks."},{"time":149599,"text":"So when a patient is having an emergency,"},{"time":151979,"text":"a doctor or a nurse at that hospital\ncan send us a WhatsApp,"},{"time":155323,"text":"telling us what they need."},{"time":156988,"text":"And then our team will immediately\nspring into action."},{"time":159777,"text":"We pull the blood from our stock,"},{"time":161479,"text":"which is delivered from the National\nCenter for Blood Transfusion;"},{"time":164694,"text":"we scan the blood into our system"},{"time":166556,"text":"so the Ministry of Health\nknows where the blood is going;"},{"time":169673,"text":"and then we'll basically\npack it into a Zip,"},{"time":171956,"text":"which is what we call\nthese little autonomous airplanes"},{"time":174700,"text":"that run on batteries."},{"time":176035,"text":"And then once that Zip is ready to go,"},{"time":178074,"text":"we accelerate it from zero\nto 100 kilometers an hour"},{"time":181305,"text":"in about half of a second."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186711,"text":"(Audience) Whoa!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":187892,"text":"And from the moment it leaves\nthe end of the launcher,"},{"time":190600,"text":"it's completely autonomous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192000,"text":"(Video: Air traffic controller\ndirects traffic)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":194886,"text":"This is our air traffic\ncontroller calling it in"},{"time":197289,"text":"to Kigali International Airport."},{"time":199155,"text":"And when the Zip arrives at the hospital,"},{"time":201132,"text":"it descends to about 30 feet\nand drops the package."},{"time":203880,"text":"We use a really simple paper parachute --\nsimple things are best --"},{"time":207454,"text":"that allows the package to come\nto the ground gently and reliably"},{"time":210527,"text":"in the same place every time."},{"time":212425,"text":"So it's just like ride sharing;"},{"time":214783,"text":"the doctors get a text message\none minute before we arrive, saying,"},{"time":218073,"text":"\"Walk outside and receive your delivery.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":220055,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":221146,"text":"And then --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":222525,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":229892,"text":"and then the doctors have what they need\nto save a patient's life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233554,"text":"This is actually watching a delivery\nhappen from our distribution center;"},{"time":237395,"text":"this vehicle is about 50 kilometers away."},{"time":240042,"text":"We're able to watch the vehicle\nas it makes a delivery at a hospital"},{"time":244097,"text":"in real time."},{"time":245310,"text":"You may have noticed there are pings"},{"time":247564,"text":"that are coming off\nof that vehicle on the screen."},{"time":250140,"text":"Those pings are actually data packets"},{"time":251941,"text":"that we're getting\nover the cell phone networks."},{"time":254246,"text":"So these planes have SIM cards\njust like your cell phone does,"},{"time":257456,"text":"and they're communicating\nover the cell network"},{"time":259681,"text":"to tell us where they are\nand how they're doing at all times."},{"time":262584,"text":"Believe it or not,\nwe actually buy family plans --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":265028,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":266062,"text":"for this fleet of vehicles,"},{"time":267442,"text":"because that's how we get the best rates."}]},{"cues":[{"time":269513,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":270620,"text":"It's actually not a joke."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272060,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":275700,"text":"So today, we're delivering\nabout 20 percent"},{"time":279024,"text":"of the national blood supply of Rwanda"},{"time":281286,"text":"outside of Kigali."},{"time":283339,"text":"We serve about 12 hospitals,"},{"time":285037,"text":"and we're adding hospitals to that network\nat an accelerating rate."},{"time":288573,"text":"All of those hospitals only receive\nblood in this way,"},{"time":291599,"text":"and most of those hospitals\nactually place multiple orders every day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297289,"text":"So the reason --"},{"time":298509,"text":"in all of health care logistics,"},{"time":300059,"text":"you're always trading off\nwaste against access."},{"time":303637,"text":"So if you want to solve waste,\nyou keep everything centralized."},{"time":307732,"text":"As a result, when patients\nare having emergencies,"},{"time":310746,"text":"sometimes they don't have\nthe medical product they need."},{"time":313860,"text":"If you want to solve access, you stock\na lot of medicine at the last mile,"},{"time":317363,"text":"at hospitals or health centers,"},{"time":318908,"text":"and then patients have\nthe medicine they need."},{"time":321096,"text":"But you end up throwing\na lot of medicine out,"},{"time":323292,"text":"which is very expensive."},{"time":324519,"text":"What's so amazing is that the Rwandan\ngovernment has been able"},{"time":327488,"text":"to break this cycle permanently."},{"time":329983,"text":"Because doctors can get\nwhat they need instantly,"},{"time":333455,"text":"they actually stock\nless blood at the hospitals."},{"time":336818,"text":"So although use of blood products\nhas increased substantially"},{"time":340652,"text":"at all the hospitals we serve,"},{"time":342357,"text":"in the last nine months,\nzero units of blood have expired"},{"time":346442,"text":"at any of these hospitals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":348579,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":354666,"text":"That's an amazing result."},{"time":356535,"text":"That's actually not been achieved\nby any other health care system"},{"time":359687,"text":"on the planet,"},{"time":360865,"text":"and it happened here."},{"time":363375,"text":"But obviously, when we're talking about\ndelivering medical products instantly,"},{"time":367801,"text":"the most important thing is patients."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370267,"text":"Let me give you an example."},{"time":372550,"text":"A couple months ago, a 24-year-old mother\ncame into one of the hospitals"},{"time":376198,"text":"that we serve,"},{"time":377390,"text":"and she gave birth via C-section."},{"time":379749,"text":"But that led to complications,\nand she started to bleed."},{"time":383366,"text":"Luckily, the doctors had some blood\nof her blood type on hand"},{"time":387282,"text":"that had been delivered\nvia Zipline's routine service,"},{"time":390266,"text":"and so they transfused her\nwith a couple units of blood."},{"time":393317,"text":"But she bled out of those units\nin about 10 minutes."},{"time":397199,"text":"In this case, that mother's life\nis in grave danger --"},{"time":401529,"text":"in any hospital in the world."},{"time":404952,"text":"But luckily, the doctors\nwho were taking care of her"},{"time":407917,"text":"immediately called\nour distribution center,"},{"time":410318,"text":"they placed an emergency order,"},{"time":412432,"text":"and our team actually did emergency\ndelivery after emergency delivery"},{"time":416868,"text":"after emergency delivery."},{"time":418590,"text":"They ended up sending\nseven units of red blood cells,"},{"time":421158,"text":"four units of plasma"},{"time":422496,"text":"and two units of platelets."},{"time":423845,"text":"That's more blood than you have\nin your entire body."},{"time":427164,"text":"All of it was transfused into her,"},{"time":429242,"text":"the doctors were able to stabilize her,"},{"time":431425,"text":"and she is healthy today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":434095,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":440645,"text":"Since we launched, we've done about 400\nemergency deliveries like that,"},{"time":445541,"text":"and there's a story like that one\nbehind most of those emergencies."},{"time":448828,"text":"Here are just a couple of the moms"},{"time":450691,"text":"who have received transfusions in this way"},{"time":452860,"text":"in the last couple months."},{"time":455132,"text":"We're always reminded: when we can help\na doctor save a mom's life,"},{"time":459256,"text":"it's not just her life that you're saving."},{"time":461755,"text":"That's also a baby boy or a baby girl"},{"time":464870,"text":"who has a mother while they're growing up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468757,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":473507,"text":"But I want to be clear:"},{"time":474778,"text":"postpartum hemorrhaging --\nit's not a Rwanda problem,"},{"time":477384,"text":"it's not a developing-world problem --"},{"time":479255,"text":"this is a global problem."},{"time":480500,"text":"Maternal health is a challenge everywhere."},{"time":482585,"text":"The main difference is that\nRwanda was the first country"},{"time":485532,"text":"to use radical technology\nto do something about it."},{"time":488783,"text":"And that's the reason this attitude\nof Africa being disrupted"},{"time":493111,"text":"or advanced technology not working here"},{"time":495048,"text":"or needing aid"},{"time":496250,"text":"is so totally wrong."},{"time":497659,"text":"Africa can be the disrupter."},{"time":500423,"text":"These small, agile, developing economies\ncan out-innovate large, rich ones."},{"time":505706,"text":"And they can totally leapfrog over\nthe absence of legacy infrastructure"},{"time":509610,"text":"to go straight to newer\nand better systems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":512237,"text":"In 2000,"},{"time":513703,"text":"if you had said that high-quality\ncellular networks were about to roll out"},{"time":517543,"text":"across all of Africa,"},{"time":518803,"text":"people would have told you\nthat you were crazy."},{"time":521493,"text":"And yet, no one anticipated"},{"time":524493,"text":"how fast those networks were going\nto connect and empower people."},{"time":528951,"text":"Today, 44 percent of the GDP of Kenya\nflows through M-Pesa,"},{"time":532901,"text":"their mobile payment platform."},{"time":534598,"text":"And not only that,"},{"time":535930,"text":"but our autonomous fleet of vehicles\nrelies on that cellular network."},{"time":539550,"text":"Over the next few years as we start\nserving private health care facilities,"},{"time":543468,"text":"we'll also use that mobile\npayment platform"},{"time":545762,"text":"to collect fees for deliveries."},{"time":547965,"text":"So innovation leads to more innovation\nleads to more innovation."},{"time":551774,"text":"And meanwhile,"},{"time":553653,"text":"most people who live\nin developed economies"},{"time":556683,"text":"think that drone delivery\nis technologically impossible,"},{"time":560477,"text":"let alone happening\nat national scale in East Africa."},{"time":564335,"text":"And I do mean East Africa,\nnot just Rwanda."}]},{"cues":[{"time":568483,"text":"On Thursday, just a couple days ago,"},{"time":570777,"text":"the Tanzanian Ministry of Health announced"},{"time":573360,"text":"that they are going to use\nthis same technology"},{"time":576116,"text":"to provide instant delivery\nof a wide range of medical products"},{"time":579728,"text":"to 10 million of the hardest to reach\npeople in the country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":583789,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":590387,"text":"It's actually going to be the largest\nautonomous system anywhere in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594625,"text":"To give you a sense\nof what this looks like,"},{"time":596748,"text":"this is one of the first\ndistribution centers."},{"time":598970,"text":"You can see a 75-kilometer service radius\naround the distribution center,"},{"time":602548,"text":"and that allows us to serve hundreds\nof health facilities and hospitals,"},{"time":606120,"text":"all of which are rural,"},{"time":607410,"text":"from that single distribution center."},{"time":609327,"text":"But to serve over 20 percent\nof the population of Tanzania,"},{"time":612387,"text":"we're going to need\nmultiple distribution centers."},{"time":614870,"text":"We'll actually need four."},{"time":616235,"text":"And from these distribution centers,"},{"time":618296,"text":"we expect to be doing several hundred\nlifesaving deliveries every day,"},{"time":623558,"text":"and this system will ultimately serve\nover 1,000 health facilities"},{"time":627821,"text":"and hospitals in the country."},{"time":629695,"text":"So yeah, East Africa\nis moving really fast."}]},{"cues":[{"time":635179,"text":"One thing that people, I think, often miss"},{"time":637987,"text":"is that these kinds of leaps\ngenerate compounding gains."},{"time":641243,"text":"For example, Rwanda, by investing\nin this infrastructure for health care,"},{"time":645852,"text":"now has an aerial logistics network\nthat they can use"},{"time":649761,"text":"to catalyze other parts of their economy,"},{"time":653168,"text":"like agriculture or e-commerce."},{"time":655254,"text":"Even more importantly,"},{"time":656565,"text":"100 percent of the teams we hire\nat these distribution centers are local."},{"time":661881,"text":"So here's our Rwandan team,"},{"time":663585,"text":"which is a group of extraordinary\nengineers and operators."},{"time":667489,"text":"They run the world's only\nautomated delivery system"},{"time":672816,"text":"operating at national scale."},{"time":675099,"text":"They have been able to master something"},{"time":677326,"text":"that the largest technology\ncompanies in the world"},{"time":680223,"text":"have not yet been able to figure out."},{"time":682679,"text":"So they are total heroes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684300,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":689015,"text":"They're total heroes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":690971,"text":"Our team's mission is to deliver\nbasic access to medicine"},{"time":695409,"text":"to all seven billion people on the planet,"},{"time":697522,"text":"no matter how hard it is to reach them."},{"time":699785,"text":"We often tell people about that mission,"},{"time":701764,"text":"and they say, \"That's so generous\nof you, it's so philanthropic.\""},{"time":704907,"text":"No!"},{"time":706293,"text":"Philanthropy has nothing to do with it."},{"time":708347,"text":"Because of the commercial contracts\nthat we sign with ministries of health,"},{"time":711985,"text":"these networks are 100 percent\nsustainable and scalable."},{"time":716019,"text":"And the reason we feel so strongly\nabout correcting that misperception"},{"time":719606,"text":"is that entrepreneurship\nis the only force in human history"},{"time":722685,"text":"that has lifted millions\nof people out of poverty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725430,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":729987,"text":"No amount of foreign aid\nis going to sustainably employ"},{"time":733884,"text":"250 million African youth."},{"time":738734,"text":"And the jobs that these kids\nmay have gotten 10 years ago"},{"time":743226,"text":"are largely being automated"},{"time":744688,"text":"or are being changed\ndramatically by technology."},{"time":747169,"text":"So they are looking for new skill sets,"},{"time":749355,"text":"new competitive advantages."},{"time":750947,"text":"They're looking for start-ups."},{"time":753097,"text":"So why aren't there more start-ups\nthat are tackling these global problems"},{"time":758817,"text":"that are faced by billions of people\nin developing economies?"},{"time":762933,"text":"The reason is that investors\nand entrepreneurs are totally blind"},{"time":766021,"text":"to the opportunity."},{"time":767323,"text":"We think these problems are the domain\nof NGOs or governments,"},{"time":771700,"text":"not private companies."},{"time":773262,"text":"That's what we have to change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":777693,"text":"You may have noticed\nI left something out of the video"},{"time":780504,"text":"that I showed you."},{"time":782054,"text":"I didn't show you how the planes land"},{"time":783923,"text":"when they get back\nto the distribution center."},{"time":786496,"text":"So, it might be obvious to you:"},{"time":789200,"text":"none of our planes have landing gear."},{"time":791036,"text":"We also don't have runways\nwhere we operate."},{"time":793156,"text":"So we have to be able\nto decelerate the plane"},{"time":795390,"text":"from about 100 kilometers an hour\nto zero in half of a second."},{"time":798786,"text":"And the way we do that"},{"time":800380,"text":"is we actually use a wire that tracks\nthat plane as it comes in,"},{"time":804152,"text":"with centimeter-level accuracy."},{"time":805989,"text":"We snag the plane out of the sky,"},{"time":808124,"text":"and then we gently plop it\nonto an actively inflated cushion."},{"time":812419,"text":"This is basically a combination\nof an aircraft carrier"},{"time":815094,"text":"and a bouncy castle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":816286,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":818063,"text":"So let me show you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":826060,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":828773,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":834990,"text":"And it might be obvious to you\nwhy I wanted to end with this video."},{"time":838250,"text":"I wanted to show you the kids\nand the teenagers"},{"time":840481,"text":"who line up on the fence every day."},{"time":843509,"text":"They cheer every launch and every landing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":846219,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":847553,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":852436,"text":"Sometimes I actually show up\nat the distribution center early"},{"time":855334,"text":"because I'm jet-lagged."},{"time":856522,"text":"I'll show up an hour before\nwe begin operation."},{"time":858839,"text":"And there will be kids on the fence\ngetting good seats."}]},{"cues":[{"time":861503,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":862737,"text":"And you go up and you ask them,"},{"time":864287,"text":"\"What do you think about the planes?\""},{"time":866130,"text":"And they'll say, \"Oh,\nit's a sky ambulance.\""},{"time":869757,"text":"So they get it."},{"time":870932,"text":"I mean, they get it more than most adults."}]},{"cues":[{"time":873917,"text":"So I was asking earlier:"},{"time":875209,"text":"Who is going to be creating the disruptive\ntechnology companies of Africa"},{"time":880991,"text":"over the next decade?"},{"time":882987,"text":"Ultimately, it's going\nto be up to these kids."},{"time":886694,"text":"They are the engineers\nof Rwanda and Africa."},{"time":890997,"text":"They are the engineers\nof our shared future."},{"time":895326,"text":"But the only way they can build\nthat future is if we realize"},{"time":899108,"text":"that world-changing companies\ncan scale in Africa,"},{"time":902615,"text":"and that disruptive technology\ncan start here first."}]},{"cues":[{"time":906822,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":907997,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}